### ğŸ” In breve

| Tipo            | Libreria                  | Comando    | Cartella                         |
| --------------- | ------------------------- | ---------- | -------------------------------- |
| ğŸ§± **Backend**  | Jest + Supertest          | `npm test` | `backend/tests/`                 |
